   <body>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC88be47e825a4100582bab7cf0bc2f3d2"></a>Removal of the starter motor idler gear
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16740"> </a>Remove the oil sump guard (<a href="78006.html#DUCdebde6802aa910058bbaf20939ae18d2">Removing the oil sump guard</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16745"> </a>Drain the engine oil (<a href="77245.html#DUCc57ed0d029f510058c2bed44952c77d2">Changing engine oil and filter cartridge</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16750"> </a>Remove the sprocket cover (<a href="79974.html#DUC678e5bc82b2410058de4ee3905e05ec4">Removing the front sprocket</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16755"> </a>Remove the clutch slave cylinder (<a href="78738.html#DUC1e4714c82b2410058cedd30e2bfae6c4">Removing the clutch slave cylinder</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16760"> </a>Drain the cooling system (<a href="77257.html#DUCf34a5aa829f91005800d816ce97b3fd2">Changing the coolant</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16765"> </a>Remove the pump-cylinder hoses (<a href="45114.html#DUCad1f8410256a10058d3dd14d9928c7d2">Removing the cylinder/piston assembly</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16770"> </a>Remove the water pump/radiator pipes (<a href="44924.html#DUCc06658c8250110058a838a10427928d2">Removing cooling system pipes and unions</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16775"> </a>Remove the generator cover and the flywheel/generator unit (<a href="45174.html#DUCf616ff28259110058912eb60359b4bd2">Removing the generator cover</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16781"> </a>Slide the gear pin (1) complete with gear (2) and washer (3).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/warning.jpg">Warning
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16784"> </a>Pay attention to the washer since it may fall inside the crankcase half.
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_046102201.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_046202202.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16791"> </a>At this point, it is possible to remove the starter motor as described in Sect.&nbsp;Starter Motor.
         </div>
      </div>
